{"tid":1372602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南邊圍村村佬有野想講","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:44:21.000Z","uid":3177,"like":4,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a21d9d64cf189e9a30bb44ddcbee5c60718c1d28","tid":1372602,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"朋友剛才最後留守既前線喺南邊圍村口<br />\n<br />\n////////<br />\n<br />\n剛同個圍村佬吹左陣水<br />\n佢話南西邊圍兩條村之外，附近既圍村村民都好不爽哩次白衫打人既事。<br />\n其實條村好多屋都租左俾南亞人同外人，所以住入面啲圍村佬唔多，所以入村其實唔難，繼而推論何妖單野可能真係勇武做。<br />\n同埋警黑合作嗰日，佢4點幾親眼見到有四五架大巴，車啲南亞佬落黎入村食飯。<br />\n佢話有一半都係南亞人，<br />\n基本上得部份係本地人，企前面做show駁上鏡。<br />\n<br />\n////////<br />\n<br />\n講就咁講<br />\n<br />\n留低既義士小心！"},{"pid":"c7cc7b46dd65409e6c6a1d0ae4332ba263ec7b26","tid":1372602,"uid":61724,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"吹你老母就吹 西鐵打人d片有撚南亞佬咩 個個本地人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11394ae9afa925a07fb05fe9f87ac12d2fa59082","tid":1372602,"uid":113922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"bca9036b5ad2cf3041ef6e256d09c2f6abbef972","tid":1372602,"uid":131637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:06:15.000Z","msg":"耳聽為虛，眼見為實，唔信短片，信人吹水？"},{"pid":"7c38b966c3994db5e98dfba2733a2f3c4bd8f3c2","tid":1372602,"uid":20059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔好比人分化  快入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372487</a><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"53214a81b299b67092b469876a1e4925951f477b","tid":1372602,"uid":17642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:07:46.000Z","msg":"721南亞人少過唐狗好多囉"},{"pid":"f54f